    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by rwinch on Fri, 2013-03-08 11:07        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last active"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
" class="active">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>I'd like to congratulate <a href="http://fi.linkedin.com/in/vschafer/">Vladimír Schäfer</a> on the release of Spring Security SAML 1.0.0.RC2. Please use the links below for additional details.</p>
